metadata.name: Medusa
metadata.description:
Soft but dangerous, beautiful but poisonous, simple yet complex, just shinning through the dark. 

If I were to become strong as steel, hard as concrete, cold as rock, could it still hurt me? 

Can I fight at all or should I embrace it until we eat each other...





/3DSMax, Zbrush, Substance Painter, Unreal Engine and Adobe Photoshop, 2022.
1024x1024/
